<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5635774>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Habitus images of Pilophorus spp. A. P. boninanus, holotype male, dorsal view (AMNH_PBI 00380692). B. Same, left lateral view (abdomen removed for dissection). C. Same, paratype female (00380693). D. Same, lateral view. E. P. miyamotoi, male (from Hokkaido, Japan). F. P. setulosus, female (Hokkaido)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5635774/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5635776>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Male genitalia of Japanese Pilophorus spp. A−B. P. boninanus, holotype (AMNH_PBI 00380692). C−E. Same, P. miyamotoi (from Shikoku, Japan). F−G. P. setulosus, female (Hokkaido). A & C. Left paramere. B. Phallotheca + vesica (endosoma). E & G. Vesica. D & F. Phallotheca." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5635776/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

